{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hey there! Welcome to the demo page for Bugtopia! This version includes certain parts of the full game, offering you several hours of gameplay! If you enjoy this demo, don't forget to leave your valuable feedback to help us speed up the release of the full version! Thank you for reading this far! The bugs can\u2019t wait to meet you! \ud83d\udc1e\ud83d\udc0c\ud83d\udc1c\ud83e\udd97\ud83e\udd8b\ud83d\udc1b\ud83d\udd77\ud83e\udd82\ud83d\udc1d\ud83e\udd9f</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bugtopia is a relaxing idle game where you can raise and breed your insects, creating a perfect eco-box environment for them. Collect a vast array of decorations and insects, and purchase tools to enhance customization or make your breeding work easier! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464890/extras/\u866b\u866b\u591a\u6837\u6027\u5c55\u793a.gif?t=1737927045\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the money earned from insects to buy more insects </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nearly a hundred insects based on real prototypes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Breed to cultivate rare species </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hundreds of decorations with different appearances </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Offline growth and transformation </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your own eco-box </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Integrated Pomodoro timer function related to gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464890/extras/\u7ed3\u8bed_EN.png?t=1737927045\" /> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464890/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737927045"